k ",[37,58,59],{},"Language & region",[17,61,62],{},[51,63],{"alt":59,"src":64},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202104081724.png",[17,66,67,68,71],{},"Pick your language from the dropdown — I'm using ",[37,69,70],{},"繁體中文 (Traditional Chinese)"," as the example, but Slack supports plenty of others:",[17,73,74],{},[51,75],{"alt":76,"src":77},"Select Traditional Chinese","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202104081726.png",[17,79,80],{},"Channels now display in the chosen language:",[17,82,83],{},[51,84],{"alt":85,"src":86},"Slack in Traditional Chinese","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202104081728.png",[12,88,90],{"id":89},"side-note","Side note",[17,92,93],{},"Slack also has a Traditional Chinese-localized marketing site if that's relevant:",[17,95,96],{},[28,97,98],{"href":98,"rel":99},"https:\u002F\u002Fslack.com\u002Fintl\u002Fzh-tw\u002F",[100],"nofollow",{"title":102,"searchDepth":103,"depth":103,"links":104},"",2,[105,106,107],{"id":14,"depth":103,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":103,"text":23},{"id":89,"depth":103,"text":90},"Misc","2021-04-08 17:17:30","Quick note on changing Slack's UI language. Each Slack workspace has its own language setting, so the change applies per workspace — not globally across your Slack account. Useful if you want to switch a workspace into Traditional Chinese, Spanish, or any other supported language.","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002Fchange-slack-ui-language","1",{"title":6,"description":110},false,"en\u002FMisc\u002Fchange-slack-ui-language",[121,122],"Slack","Software",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2021\u002F04\u002F08\u002Fchange-slack-ui-language\u002F","90KwYn9yOFow9Pz2KuA6_l61A3fggPqGGALZj5o0AHg",{"newer":127,"older":131},{"url":128,"title":129,"date":130},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F04\u002F11\u002Fpip-command-not-found-fix\u002F","`command not found: pip` or `pip3` — Quick Fix","2021-04-11